UI Redesign Prompt

Prompt:

You are a senior UX/UI designer specializing in modern AI SaaS dashboards.

Redesign the following chatbot interface for a financial AI assistant called FinMAG AI, which is connected to a live data warehouse.

🎯 Goal

Transform the current layout into a modern, premium AI workspace that feels:

highly professional (enterprise SaaS)
clean and minimal
interactive and dynamic
focused on data + chat fusion (not just messaging)
🧠 Context

The app provides real-time financial insights:

revenue (CA)
treasury (trésorerie)
stock levels
client risk analysis
accounting anomalies

The assistant should feel like a financial copilot, not a simple chatbot.

🧱 Current Problems to Fix
Layout feels too spaced out and empty
Chat is not the main focus
Suggestions look repetitive and static
Input bar feels basic
No strong hierarchy between dashboard elements
Lack of visual depth and modern UI polish
🎨 Required Improvements
1. Layout Structure

Redesign into:

Left sidebar (navigation + history + quick analytics)
Main chat workspace (center focus)
Optional right panel for insights or KPI summaries
2. Chat Experience
Use modern chat bubbles (AI vs user clearly differentiated)
Add smooth message animations
Improve readability (max width, spacing, typography)
AI messages should support structured blocks (not only text)
3. AI Response Format (IMPORTANT)

AI responses must support:

KPI cards (revenue, stock alerts, risk clients)
mini tables
alert badges
charts placeholders
structured financial insights

Make responses feel like a data dashboard inside chat

4. Suggestions Section

Replace static suggestion cards with:

categorized quick actions
shorter labels
hover animations
better grouping (Finance / Stock / Clients / Alerts)
5. Input Bar

Redesign to feel premium:

floating input design
attachment button + optional voice icon
glowing focus state
gradient or soft glass effect
modern send button
6. Visual Style
modern SaaS design
soft shadows + glassmorphism
light neutral background with subtle gradient
strong primary accent color (blue or indigo recommended)
smooth rounded corners (12–16px)
consistent spacing system (8pt grid)
7. Motion & Interaction

Add:

hover elevation effects
smooth transitions (150–250ms)
typing indicator for AI
subtle loading states
micro-interactions for buttons/cards
🧩 Output Required

Provide:

a redesigned layout description
component structure (React or UI components)
visual hierarchy explanation
optionally a sample React + Tailwind layout
🚀 Final Vision

The result should feel like:

“Bloomberg Terminal × ChatGPT × Modern SaaS dashboard”